                </p>
        </div>
        <div class="span3 subPoint">
                <img src="/images/yelp_logo.png" alt="Yelp logo" width="133.2" height="100">
                <h3>Make Reservations</h3>
                <p>
                    Get hotel and restaurant recommendations and driving directions.
                </p>
        </div>
        <div class="span3 subPoint">
                <img src="/images/social.png" alt="Connect" width="100" height="100">
